PORT=Port number of the server. (optional)
BILIBILI_COOKIE=Cookie for Bilibili (optional)
PROXY=Proxies for requests (optional) (e.g. ["https://proxy1.com", "https://proxy2.com"])
REDIS_HOST=Redis host (optional)
REDIS_PORT=Redis port (optional)
REDIS_PASSWORD=Redis password (optional)
NINE_ANIME_HELPER_URL=9anime resolver/helper URL (optional, required for some VRF flows)
NINE_ANIME_HELPER_KEY=9anime helper API key (optional)
NINE_ANIME_BASE_URL=9anime mirror base URL (optional) (default: https://9animetv.be)
NINE_ANIME_PROXY=HTTP proxy URL for 9anime requests (optional)
NINE_ANIME_PROXY_KEY=Proxy API key if your proxy expects it (optional)
TMDB_KEY=TMDB access token auth (optional)
RECAPTCHATOKEN=Gogoanime recaptcha token (optional)
GOGOANIME_URL=Gogoanime base url (optional)
ZORO_URL=Zoro custom url (optional)
ANIMEKAI_URL=Animekai custom url (optional)
MULTIMOVIES_URL=Multimovies custom url (optional)
NODE_ENV=Environment (optional) (DEMO or PROD)
